race.comment: Tricky race to line up with all of these babies facing the starter for the first time. Local BETTER BLITZEM (1) has looked handy winning both trials to date around this circuit and Holt stays on board for race day. Expected to go well on debut. ALBERTA BOUND (6) saluted in a recent Cairns trial by over six lengths and looks to have plenty of ability. Rates among the leading hopes. MISS SO AND SO (7) won a Mackay trial by a whopping 14 lengths and only needs some luck from the wide draw to be playing a role in the outcome. STYLISH DIAMOND (8) is another recent trial winner and any market confidence must be noted. BOOMIOUS (3) next in line.
